data.description: Welcome home to 4009 Tranquility Ct in Monrovia. Nestled on almost 1 acre, this 3 bedroom, 2 and a half bath rancher feels like a private oasis, whilst still maintaining great commuter access! Upon entering, you are greeted by gleaming floors, an updated kitchen, and a spacious family room with wood burning fireplace. Enjoy the mature landscaping and tranquil sounds of Mother Nature off the large back deck! The main level also hosts the primary suite with updated bathroom, two additional bedrooms, and an updated hallway full bathroom. The lower level is spacious, walk-out level, and hosts a half bathroom that could be completed into a full. The lower level has tons of space for an additional room, storage, workshop, den/recreation  room, etc. Bring your imagination to complete this lower level. Home boasts newer Anderson windows.
